name: chubby-girls-golden
description:
IMPORTANT: Use anythingv3's vae for this. Can be found at:

https://huggingface.co/Linaqruf/anything-v3.0/blob/main/Anything-V3.0.vae.pt

Works incredibly well generating chubby and fat girls of all sizes. Provides a level of detail not seen in other chubby models. Based on Elysium, biggergirls and anythingv3, it responds to the same trigger words.


Features:
-HIGH level of detail

-Excellent hands

-Great belly grabs with a combination of hand on own stomach and deep skin

-Works in many different poses

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: Using a better version of biggergirls and a new method to mix models, with a little bit of training of my own. Still responsive to prior commands. Seems to be overall better at bellies, and I've beaten it into consistency on faces, etc., which it seemed to be a little overcooked on.
